ID: US-101
Title: Browse products
Story: As any user, I want to browse product categories so that I can explore different items available.

ID: US-102
Title: Support Multilingual Users
Story: As a user, I want to switch between multiple languages on the platform so that I can use the website in my preferred language.

ID: US-201
Title: Buyer Account Creation 
Story: As a buyer, I want to create an account that can buy products.

ID: US-202
Title: View Product Information
Story: As a buyer, I want to view detailed information about a product when I select it so that I can make informed purchase decisions.

ID: US-203
Title: Compare Products
Story: As a buyer, I want to compare the information and prices of two selected products so that I can choose the best option.

ID: US-204
Title: Filter Products
Story: As a buyer, I want to filter products based on criteria such as price and quantity so that I can find products that meet my specific needs.

ID: US-205
Title: Add to cart
Story: As a buyer, I want to add items to my shopping cart so that I can purchase multiple products at once.

ID: US-206
Title: Proceed to Checkout
Story: As a buyer, I want to proceed to checkout from my cart so that I can complete my purchase.

ID: US-207
Title: Track order
Story: As a buyer, I want to track my order status so that I know when my purchase will be delivered.

ID: US-208
Title: Write product review
Story: As a buyer, I want to write a review for a purchased product so that I can share my experience with others.

ID: US-209
Title: Remove from Cart
Story: As a buyer, I want to remove items from my shopping cart so that I can modify my selection before purchase.

ID: US-210
Title: Update Cart Quantity
Story: As a buyer, I want to change the quantity of items in my cart so that I can adjust the number of products I want to buy.

ID: US-211
Title: Confirm Purchase
Story: As a buyer, I want to confirm my purchase and receive a receipt so that I can finalize my order and be informed of the arrival date.

ID: US-301
Title: Seller Account Creation
Story: As a registered business (seller), I want to be able to be confirmed as a business by the software engineers/website and be able to sell products I have.

ID: US-302
Title: List products for sale
Story: As a registered business, I want to add new products for sale so that customers can purchase them from the store.

ID: US-303
Title: Manage inventory
Story: As a registered business, I want to update my inventory levels so that customers can see the availability of my products.

ID: US-304
Title: View sales reports
Story: As a registered business, I want to access sales data so that I can analyze my performance over time.

ID: US-305
Title: Handle returns
Story: As a registered business I want to process return requests so that I can handle product returns efficiently.

ID: US-306
Title: Update Product Information
Story: As a registered business, I want to add, update, or remove product listings so that customers can view accurate and current information.

ID: US-401
Title: Admin Account Creation
Story: As an admin, I would like to receive an account by the software engineers made purposefully for admins to handle the website.

ID: US-402
Title: Manage product listings
Story: As an admin, I want to add, update, or delete product listings so that I can keep the inventory current.

ID: US-403
Title: Monitor site activity
Story: As an admin, I want to view site analytics so that I can track sales performance and user activity.

ID: US-404
Title: Handle customer complaints
Story: As an admin, I want to manage customer support requests so that I can resolve issues efficiently.

ID: US-405
Title: Manage promotions
Story: As an admin, I want to create and update promotional offers so that I can boost sales during special events.

ID: US-406
Title: Maintain Data Security
Story: As an admin, I want to ensure that all customer data is encrypted and securely stored so that we comply with data protection regulations and protect user privacy.

ID: US-407
Title: Ensure Website Accessibility
Story: As an admin, I want the website to be accessible to all users, including those with disabilities, so that everyone can use the platform effectively.

ID: US-408
Title: Monitor Website Performance
Story: As an admin, I want to ensure that the website performs well during high-traffic periods so that users have a smooth shopping experience.